Plot: The Eisner Award-winning 12-issue series from Grant Morrison and Frank Quitely is available in Absolute format! The Man of Steel battles Bizarro, Zibarro and more before facing the final revenge of Lex Luthor. Plus: a bonus sketchbook section and more!
Characters: Perry White, Lex Luthor, Bizarro #1, Lana Lang, Krypto, Lois Lane, Jonathan Kent, Martha Clark Kent, Jimmy Olsen, Superman
